Panwrite Plastic Industries Sdn. Bhd.
Panwrite Plastic Industries Sdn Bhd (Panwrite) is a well-established Malaysian manufacturer with over 30 years of experience specializing in high-quality plastic packaging solutions for the personal care, household, pharmaceutical and industrial sectors. ISO9001:2015 certified, Panwrite has earned a strong reputation for reliability, technical excellence, and customer-focused innovation.

Panwrite offers a complete range of plastic packaging products, including High-Density Polyethylene (HDPE) bottles, Polyethylene Terephthalate (PET) bottles, custom-designed cap closures, and flexible packaging solutions. It is the only manufacturer in Malaysia that provides in-line UV silkscreen printing directly onto PET bottles, allowing for faster turnaround and high-end brand presentation.

The Company offers a comprehensive range of value-added services including labelling, shrinkwrap packaging and product assembly, making it a one-stop packaging provider. Equipped with advanced moulding technologies and a skilled technical team, Panwrite serves OEM and contract manufacturing clients locally and is expanding into regional markets, supported by close collboration with mould makers like M3 for custom packaging solutions.

As part of its commitment to sustainability, Panwrite actively develops packaging solutions incorporating Post-Consumer Recycled (PCR) resins and biodegradable materials —helping customers achieve both performance and environmental responsibility.

Business Interests:
Panwrite is actively seeking for global partnerships, particularly with OEMs, ODMs, and brand owners in the personal care, cosmetics, healthcare, and household sectors to supply HDPE and PET bottles, jars and closures. The company offers customised moulding and tooling services, in-house UV silkscreen printing, labelling and shrinkwrap solutions to deliver ready-to-fill packaging. Panwrite is also focused on sustainable packaging development, exploring bio-based and recyclable materials, and is keen to expand its presence in ASEAN and international markets through strategic distribution partnerships.
